<p class="ql-align-center"> 活动现场抽奖福利多多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/b489e9ff5b584a36b3b01d6c29325dd7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
